Boulevard will begin within the next two months. RANDY LEFFINGWELL / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, "Missiles and snow cones" have given way to more subdued 
fashions (above). ; Photo, Left, "a Little Bear"; ; Photo, right, man's tank 
top. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
TOWNSON, GEORGE; FREDERICK'S OF HOLLYWOOD; CORPORATE RESTRUCTURING; CLOTHING; 
FASHION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
