<TEXT>
<P>
Elizabeth Taylor has penned her memoirs -- but don't look for them in the 
supermarket racks any time soon. 
</P>
<P>
"Miss Taylor has in fact completed a manuscript which chronicles her life but 
there are no immediate plans for its release," according to a statement from 
